Package: stampr
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Temporal Analysis of Moving Polygons
Version: 0.1
Author: Jed Long and Colin Robertson
Maintainer: Colin Robertson <crobertson@wlu.ca>
Description: Perform spatial temporal analysis of moving polygons; a longstanding analysis problem in Geographic Information Systems. Facilitates directional analysis, shape analysis, and some other simple functionality for examining spatial-temporal patterns of moving polygons.
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10)
License: GPL-3
Imports:
    sp,
    rgeos,
    raster,
    rgdal,
    maptools,
    deldir,
    spdep,
    grDevices,
    methods
Suggests:
    igraph
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
